&lt;p&gt;For example, right now, this is what I use to make it work on
Windows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;rake 'asset:packager:create_yml' rescue run 'rake.bat
asset:packager:create_yml' capify! rescue run 'capify.bat .'&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
